OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781772507
OL,3,CEngland prepare for World Cup opener
OL,4,Cagainst Croatia
OL,6,FEngland begin their World Cup journey
OL,7,Fon Wednesday evening as they take on
OL,8,FCroatia in their first game of the
OL,9,Ftournament.
OL,11,FThousands of England fans have been
OL,12,Fflooding into Dallas, Texas, ahead of
OL,13,Fthe match, which starts at 3pm local
OL,14,Ftime and 9pm BST.
OL,16,FCroatia, ranked 11th in the world,
OL,17,Fhave been a thorn in England's side in
OL,18,Fprevious years, most famously beating
OL,19,Fthem in the semi-finals of the 2018
OL,20,FWorld Cup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
