OL,3,CEngland prepare for World Cup opener
OL,4,Cagainst Croatia
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe winner of this match is expected
OL,12,Fto take the top spot in Group L, which
OL,13,Falso includes Ghana and Panama.
OL,15,FClose to 15,000 England fans are said
OL,16,Fto have made the journey to Dallas,
OL,17,Fwhile supporters at home are expected
OL,18,Fto watch the game at late-night pub
OL,19,Fsessions across the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
