PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781772507
OL,3,CEngland prepare for World Cup opener
OL,4,Cagainst Croatia
OL,6,FDallas is one of the tournament's
OL,7,Fhottest venues, but the AT&T Stadium
OL,8,Fdoes have a roof and air-conditioning
OL,9,Fshould the teams encounter any
OL,10,Fthunderstorms or extreme heat.
OL,12,FThe match is the first international
OL,13,Ftournament game for manager Thomas
OL,14,FTuchel, whose contract was extended in
OL,15,FFebruary so that he will also lead the
OL,16,FEuros in 2028.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
