OL,3,CEngland prepare for World Cup opener
OL,4,Cagainst Croatia
OL,6,FIt does, however, include a
OL,7,Fperformance clause, which means he
OL,8,Fcould be replaced if England doesn't
OL,9,Fdo well, Football Association CEO Mark
OL,10,FBullingham said on Tuesday.
OL,12,F"There's performance clauses in every
OL,13,Fsingle contract with the FA, right?
OL,14,FI'm not going to go into any detail on
OL,15,Fwhat they are," Bullingham said.
OL,17,F"The reality is we're really confident
OL,18,Fhe's going to be our coach in 2028."
