OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781772507
OL,3,CEngland prepare for World Cup opener
OL,4,Cagainst Croatia
OL,6,FThe game comes as England's full-back
OL,7,FTino Livramento was ruled out of the
OL,8,Ftournament on Tuesday due to a calf
OL,9,Finjury sustained in training, forcing
OL,10,FTuchel into a late squad change.
OL,12,FChelsea defender Trevoh Chalobah has
OL,13,Fstepped up as a replacement, having
OL,14,Fjoined the England training camp in
OL,15,FKansas City.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
